{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4f16516f4a","title":"给黄炎培的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2ab480adcc","index":0,"year":1954,"month":12,"day":17,"articleId":"4f16516f4a"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji34","name":"毛泽东全集第34卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/34-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji34":{"comments":[{"id":"323f3fad25","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"4f16516f4a","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"惠书，指黄炎培1954年12月15日给毛泽东的信。信中谈了他于1954年11月15日去北京医院做前列腺手术的情况和最近时期工商界的情况。关子工商界的情况，信中说：自强调爱国守法以来，工商界多少有些进步，但问题还有，有些还很严重，其中中小工商业较难导向国家资本主义，而以中小商业为尤甚。河北将棉布统销和私营布商的全行业改造相结合，分为维持、转业、改造三种处理方法，是很好的典型，如果各地按其不同情况参进行，当能完成改造私营工商业的任务。大文，指黄炎培写的《关于思想问题的四点答问》一文。"}],"contents":[{"id":"7804bc5611","type":"title","text":"给黄炎培\"的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"4f16516f4a"},{"id":"323f3fad25","type":"paragraph","text":"黄先生：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"4f16516f4a"},{"id":"e14372af00","type":"paragraph","text":"惠书及大文的收到，已付几个同志传阅，须稍待方能壁还，谅为幸。顺颂","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"4f16516f4a"},{"id":"e0ebc4e445","type":"subtitle","text":"日安","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"4f16516f4a"},{"id":"64cd7d9a0a","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"4f16516f4a"},{"id":"9bf5a32591","type":"paragraph","text":"十二月十七日","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"4f16516f4a"},{"id":"a136c27c7d","type":"paragraph","text":"口黄炎培，当时任中国民主建国会主任委员、全国人大常委会副委员长。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"4f16516f4a"}],"page":{"id":"4443680596","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"4f16516f4a","start":382,"